nsure that a launch”, “, reentry site,” after “United States Government launch site”, “or reentry date commitment” after “launch date commitment”, “or reentry” after “obtained for a launch”, “, reentry site,” after “access to a launch site”, “, or services related to a reentry,” after “amount for launch services”, and “or reentry” after “the scheduled launch”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/105/303/s102/a/9/C"},"text":"Pub. L. 105–303, § 102(a)(9)(C)","children":[],"tail":", inserted “or reentry” after “prompt launching”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
